The,XE,Currency,Data,API,is,a,back,end,solution,for,tracking,real,time,exchange,rates,in,the,international,currency,markets,The,API,serves,as,a,hub,for,streaming,exchange,rates,of,over,currencies,delivered,by,more,than,sources,from,around,the,world,The,HTTPS,GET,serves,as,the,gateways,for,accessing,the,API,that,is,responsive,to,JSON,XML,CSV,protocols,The,use,of,the,XE,Currency,Data,API,attracts,a,minimum,fee,of,annually,Prices,for,different,pricing,plans,depend,on,the,request,volume,categorized,as,minimum,requests,per,month,medium,requests,per,month,and,enterprise,unlimited,request,per,month